[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    175[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             "BMI 28. No acute infections to explain the elevation. Patient has no "
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    176[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             "history of autoimmune disease. Repeat hs-CRP ordered to confirm. "
